ected Device Quarantine</p><p>Access Control: Device-based whitelist/blacklist</p><p>Wi-Fi Security: Open, WEP, WPA-PSK</p><p>Firewall Features: Open, WEP, WPA-PSK</p>', 'OTHERS SPECIFICATIONS', '<p>Certification: FCC、CE、DFS、VCCI、JRF、JPA、RoHS</p><p>Environment: Operating Temperature: 0℃~40℃ (32℉ ~104℉), Storage Temperature: -40℃~70℃ (-40℉ ~158℉), Operating Humidity: 10%~90% non-condensing, Storage Humidity: 5%~90% non-condensing</p><p>Power Supply: 100-240V 50/60Hz</p>', '2020-07-05 18:34:36', '2020-08-14 05:56:36', NULL),
